INSERT INTO `wb_posts` VALUES (1,1,'2018-04-19 05:00:46','2018-04-19 05:00:46','I wanna know what new shows you guys are really excited about.\r\n\r\nI\'m coming up a little short, myself. I\'ve got more than 20 shows in my Crunchyroll queue at the moment, and... I liked Crossing Time?\r\n\r\nOkay, Uma Musume is cheerful and entertaining, and I\'m optimistic about Golden Kamuy. I\'m a sucker for high school stories with antisocial/outsider/loser characters (the public is reminded again not to draw unseemly conclusions about my own high school life from this fact), so I have some hopes for 3d Kanojo--even though it\'s already seeming kinda sloppy.\r\n\r\nI think I\'m giving up on LoGH and Megalobox. I WANT to like them, because it makes me seem like I have cool, retro taste... but seeing the second episodes in my queue gives me an unmistakable \"oh no... do I have to?\" feeling, which is not how one ought feel about one\'s entertainment.','The Case for anime','','trash','open','open','','hello-world__trashed','','','2018-04-27 02:00:55','2018-04-27 02:00:55','',0,'http://localhost/?p=1',0,'post','',1),(4,1,'2018-04-20 00:35:39','2018-04-20 00:35:39','','Home','','publish','closed','closed','','home','','','2018-05-02 04:28:58','2018-05-02 04:28:58','',0,'http://localhost/?p=4',1,'nav_menu_item','',0),(8,1,'2018-04-20 02:31:41','2018-04-20 02:31:41','','Home Page','','publish','closed','closed','','home-page','','','2018-05-08 04:32:40','2018-05-08 04:32:40','',0,'http://localhost/?page_id=8',0,'page','',0),(9,1,'2018-04-20 02:31:41','2018-04-20 02:31:41','','Home Page','','inherit','closed','closed','','8-revision-v1','','','2018-04-20 02:31:41','2018-04-20 02:31:41','',8,'http://localhost/2018/04/20/8-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(10,1,'2018-04-20 21:06:49','2018-04-20 21:06:49','','Recent Reviews','','trash','closed','closed','','acf_recent-reviews__trashed','','','2018-04-26 19:43:19','2018-04-26 19:43:19','',0,'http://localhost/?post_type=acf&#038;p=10',0,'ac