a\'s Ran works so well; he essentially drops the double plot with Gloucester and his progeny, effectively streamlining and focusing the drama on Lear and his plight. In any case, Kozintsev is an accomplished visual director as this picture is often visibly captivating, but the adoptive tragedy that befalls so many who adapt King Lear has, as well, touched his work here. Shakespeare\'s Lear is a massive play, often touted by scholars as the finest literary experience one could take, and any director is mad to undertake an adaptation and squeeze in all what makes it so grand and immortalizing. A fine adaptation, though assuredly a flawed one.','King Lear','','publish','open','open','','king-lear','','','2018-05-16 00:24:58','2018-05-16 00:24:58','',0,'http://localhost/?p=150',0,'post','',0),(151,1,'2018-05-16 00:16:24','2018-05-16 00:16:24','','lear','','inherit','open','closed','','lear','','','2018-05-17 23:11:07','2018-05-17 23:11:07','',150,'http://localhost/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/lear.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(152,1,'2018-05-16 00:19:12','2018-05-16 00:19:12','','Lear Image','','inherit','open','closed','','lear-2','','','2018-05-16 00:19:33','2018-05-16 00:19:33','',150,'http://localhost/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/lear-1.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(153,1,'2018-05-16 00:20:37','2018-05-16 00:20:37','','lear poster','','inherit','open','closed','','lear-poster','','','2018-05-16 00:20:44','2018-05-16 00:20:44','',150,'http://localhost/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/lear-poster.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(154,1,'2018-05-16 00:23:01','2018-05-16 00:23:01','','king lear','','publish','open','closed','','king-lear','','','2018-05-16 00:23:01','2018-05-16 00:23:01','',0,'http://localhost/Enhanced Category/king-lear/',0,'enhancedcategory','',0),(155,1,'2018-05-16 00:23:01','2018-05-16 00:23:01','','1971','','publish','open','closed','','1971','','','2018-05-16 00:23:01','2018-05-16 00:23:01','',0,'http://localhost/Enhanced Category/1971/',0,